channel.title: Advertising ? Cant get Players you want?
channel.description:
So i was browsing threw google for runescape ps status page's and then i came across one ive never herd of before.
[url=http://status-checker.net46.net/]http://status-checker.net46.net/[/url]
it has information on
[ul][li]item ids[/li] [li]npc ids[/li] [li]object ids[/li][/ul]
[ul][li]it has a server status page[/li] [li]how to install java[/li] [li]how to play the actual runescape private servers[/li] [li] enwikipidia about runescape itself[/li][/ul]
it has a featured area for server but that doesnt work it looks derilict and looks as it has been for ages
but i thought i would post it to see what happens.
all the best
